Modules:

    Main windows: contains option to make improvements, view the fighters, or fight

    Team: contains the fighters during a fight

    Fighter: could be a computer or human one

    Action: could be to help friends, or damage enemies. Could be to 1, or all

    Fighting Area: manages the teams, and gives reward in case of winning


Fight flow:

    One from each team each time (starting by random team)
    If a team has less fighters, the rest of the other team fighters will act in a row
    The team that is left without any fighter loses